CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782893891
OL,3,CRetailers caught selling e-scooters
OL,4,Cfor 'commuting' despite road ban
OL,6,FUnder the current law, privately-owned
OL,7,Fe-scooters and hoverboards are banned
OL,8,Ffrom public spaces such as roads,
OL,9,Fcycle lanes and pavements, and can
OL,10,Fonly be legally used on private land.
OL,12,FBut government figures shows that up
OL,13,Fto 950,000 e-scooters are now believed
OL,14,Fto be privately owned across England
OL,15,Falone.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
