CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782893891
OL,3,CRetailers caught selling e-scooters
OL,4,Cfor 'commuting' despite road ban
OL,6,FIn 2022, after a 14-year-old girl fell
OL,7,Foff her e-scooter and died under the
OL,8,Fwheels of a minibus, a coroner
OL,9,Fcriticised retailers for selling the
OL,10,Fvehicles without proper warnings about
OL,11,Fthe law, saying that without change
OL,12,Fthere would be more deaths.
OL,14,FIn June, police forces across the
OL,15,Fcountry mounted a co-ordinated
OL,16,Fcrackdown on illegal e-scooter use,
OL,17,Fand official data shows 10 people were
OL,18,Fkilled and 1,484 injured in e-scooter
OL,19,Fcollisions last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
