OL,3,CRetailers caught selling e-scooters
OL,4,Cfor 'commuting' despite road ban
OL,6,FResearch by the Press Association has
OL,7,Fnow revealed that retailers ` from
OL,8,Fmajor brands to specialist e-scooter
OL,9,Fsellers ` have been giving customers
OL,10,Fthe impression that the vehicles can
OL,11,Fbe used on the road.
OL,13,F"Misinformation could cause misuse,
OL,14,Fputting the lives of all road users at
OL,15,Frisk", said Tanya Braun, director of
OL,16,Fexternal affairs for public safety
OL,17,Fcampaign group Living Streets.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
