OL,3,CRetailers caught selling e-scooters
OL,4,Cfor 'commuting' despite road ban
OL,6,FOn a page of the Currys website which
OL,7,Fadvertises Segway e-scooters,
OL,8,Fcustomers are told they can purchase a
OL,9,F"fun, efficient means of getting
OL,10,Faround your local area".
OL,12,FSome of the models on sale boast
OL,13,Fhigher top speeds "so you can ensure
OL,14,Fyou're not late for work", the page
OL,15,Freads.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@WO]uD@SOUvD@YO]
