OL,3,CRetailers caught selling e-scooters
OL,4,Cfor 'commuting' despite road ban
OL,6,FOn the Argos website, a page
OL,7,Fadvertising adult electric scooters
OL,8,Ffrom brands including Pure, Segway,
OL,9,FMcLaren, and Zinc suggested they offer
OL,10,F"smooth rides, whether you're gliding
OL,11,Fto work or cruising for fun".
OL,13,FIt adds: "Commuting just got a serious
OL,14,Fglow-up."
OL,16,FAmazon has on sale a #379 MIWEN
OL,17,Felectric scooter which is recommended
OL,18,Ffor "urban commuting".
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@\O]uD@JOUvD@IO]zD@EOUzD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
