OL,3,CRetailers caught selling e-scooters
OL,4,Cfor 'commuting' despite road ban
OL,6,FMs Braun said: "Consumers must be made
OL,7,Faware of the restrictions on private e-
OL,8,Fscooter use.
OL,10,F"Rental scheme operators have had the
OL,11,Fdesign of their e-scooters approved by
OL,12,Fthe Department for Transport and they
OL,13,Fknow who is using their e-scooters and
OL,14,Fwhere.
OL,16,F"In contrast, it's likely that a
OL,17,Fperson on a privately owned e-scooter
OL,18,Fwill be using a more dangerous vehicle
OL,19,Fwith higher speeds and will not be
OL,20,Finsured.
OL,26,@nD@POUrD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
