OL,3,CRetailers caught selling e-scooters
OL,4,Cfor 'commuting' despite road ban
OL,6,F"Misinformation could cause misuse,
OL,7,Fputting the lives of all road users at
OL,8,Frisk."
OL,10,FThe Press Association has also
OL,11,Freviewed advertising material from
OL,12,Fsmaller retailers, including
OL,13,Fspecialist e-scooter shops based in
OL,14,Fthe UK.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@FO]
