OL,3,CRetailers caught selling e-scooters
OL,4,Cfor 'commuting' despite road ban
OL,6,FSome are explicit in offering e-
OL,7,Fscooters for sale for "city
OL,8,Fcommuting", customers are told they
OL,9,Fcan "skip the crowds and delays" and
OL,10,Fenjoy stability and comfort "when
OL,11,Friding on city streets", and some of
OL,12,Fthe vehicle's features ` such as brake
OL,13,Flights ` are highlighted for "ensuring
OL,14,Fthat you can be seen when out and
OL,15,Fabout".
OL,26,@oD@WOUpD@JO]qD@EOUqD@`O]rD@]OUsD@WO]uD@
OL,26,A^OUwD@FO]
