OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782893891
OL,3,CRetailers caught selling e-scooters
OL,4,Cfor 'commuting' despite road ban
OL,6,FHe set out that Fatima had been riding
OL,7,Fa privately-owned e-scooter without a
OL,8,Fhelmet when she fell in front of a
OL,9,Fminibus, and reported: "Some
OL,10,Fmanufacturers and retailers of e-
OL,11,Fscooters in England and Wales provide
OL,12,Fconsumers with written warnings about
OL,13,Fthe illegal use of e-scooters, others
OL,14,Fdo not.
OL,16,F"Where such warnings are present,
OL,17,Foften they are not prominent."
OL,26,@qD@XOUxD@AOUyD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
