OL,3,CRetailers caught selling e-scooters
OL,4,Cfor 'commuting' despite road ban
OL,6,FNorthamptonshire Police launched a
OL,7,Fcrackdown on illegal e-scooter use
OL,8,Fthis month after a five-year-old boy
OL,9,Fwas knocked down and suffered a
OL,10,Ffractured skull.
OL,12,F"These vehicles may seem convenient,
OL,13,Fbut when they are used illegally or
OL,14,Firresponsibly they can pose a very
OL,15,Freal risk", said Chief Inspector
OL,16,FNathan Shepherd.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
