PN,30415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782893891
OL,3,CRetailers caught selling e-scooters
OL,4,Cfor 'commuting' despite road ban
OL,6,FArgos includes prominent warnings
OL,7,Fabout the law around e-scooters on
OL,8,Feach individual advert, and after
OL,9,Fbeing contacted by the Press
OL,10,FAssociation it edited its website to
OL,11,Fremove references in advertising
OL,12,Fmaterial to commuting.
OL,14,F"As a responsible retailer, we include
OL,15,Fclear warnings on all e-scooter
OL,16,Fproduct pages that they cannot be used
OL,17,Fon public highways, including roads
OL,18,Fand pavements", a spokesperson for
OL,19,FArgos said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782893891
OL,3,CRetailers caught selling e-scooters
OL,4,Cfor 'commuting' despite road ban
OL,6,F"We have updated wording on a search
OL,7,Fpage to replicate what we already
OL,8,Finclude on our product pages to be
OL,9,Feven more clear for our customers."
OL,11,FCurrys includes a similar legal
OL,12,Fwarning at the bottom of the product
OL,13,Finformation for the e-scooters it
OL,14,Fsells, and it is now conducting a
OL,15,Freview of its website "to make sure no
OL,16,Fproduct listings suggest e-scooters
OL,17,Fcan be used on public roads or spaces".
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@cO]wD@WOUyD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30417
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782893891
OL,3,CRetailers caught selling e-scooters
OL,4,Cfor 'commuting' despite road ban
OL,6,F"Whenever we sell an e-scooter in
OL,7,Fstore or online, we make clear to
OL,8,Fcustomers that privately-owned e-
OL,9,Fscooters can only legally be used on
OL,10,Fprivate land with the landowner's
OL,11,Fpermission," Currys added.
OL,13,FHalfords told the Press Association it
OL,14,F"provides a range of e-scooter options
OL,15,Ffor customers, with the safety and
OL,16,Flegality of these products a priority
OL,17,Fthroughout the sales process.
OL,19,F"We continue to provide clear guidance
OL,20,Fon the law relating to e-scooters both
OL,21,Fonline and in store."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@LO]vD@AOU{D@AOU}D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30418
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782893891
OL,3,CRetailers caught selling e-scooters
OL,4,Cfor 'commuting' despite road ban
OL,6,FAmazon said it has guidelines that e-
OL,7,Fscooter adverts cannot include images
OL,8,Fof riders on the roads or pavements
OL,9,Fand "must depict responsible usage in
OL,10,Faccordance with UK law", and they have
OL,11,Fto carry a legal note which states "e-
OL,12,Fscooters are prohibited from use in
OL,13,Fany public road or space in the UK".
OL,26,@qD@EOUrD@WO]sD@dOUuD@cO]
